                <li><strong>RESTRICTION:</strong> You CANNOT use another Chaos Card on the Same Turn You activate a Unification Class Chaos Card; and vice versa. All Unification Class Chaos Cards CANNOT affect the same Players two Activations in a row; regardless of who is the User and who is the Target [01.1].</li>
